Definition: In this task you will be given a list of strings and you need to concatenate them.

Positive Examples.explanation: The strings 'a', 'b', 'c', got concatenated into the string 'abc'. So this is a good example.
The two strings, 'hello' and 'world', got concatenated into one large string 'helloworld' without adding a space in the middle. So this is a good example.

Negative Examples.explanation: Not all of the string were concatenated into one string. This is a bad example.
The strings are concatenated in the wrong order. This is a bad example.
